thread.title: Dale Doring
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Dale Doring

author: Dale Doring
title: Dale Doring
text:
Arrived very soon after being ordered.The product is excellent.
The print quality is equal to that of genuine ink.
I don't see the sense in paying a premium price for a product when you can purchase a compatible cartridge for a fraction of the price and achieve the same result.
